  <prompt>Implement GET endpoints for listing jobs + per-job status. Use SystemAdmin policy. Queries sprk_backgroundjob + sprk_backgroundjobrun. Per spec.md FR-2.6.</prompt>
  <goal>GET /api/admin/jobs returns all registered jobs + status. GET /api/admin/jobs/{jobId}/status returns detailed status + last 10 runs. Both behind SystemAdmin policy.</goal>
  <constraints>
    <constraint source="ADR-008">Endpoint filter for auth — NOT global middleware</constraint>
    <constraint source="spec">Use existing SystemAdmin policy at AuthorizationModule.cs:241</constraint>
    <constraint source="bff-extensions.md §A">BFF pre-merge checklist</constraint>
  </constraints>
  <knowledge>
    <topic>admin-endpoint-pattern</topic>
    <files>
      <file>docs/adr/ADR-008-endpoint-filters.md</file>
